choices.text:
Write a sentence with twenty words about cats:

I have a cat. His name is Simon and he's a good cat.

Write a sentence with twenty words about cats:

Cats are small, furry animals that are loved by many people.

Write a sentence with twenty words about cats:

Cats are cute, cuddly, and a lot of fun to play with.

Write a sentence with twenty words about cats:

I have a cat and I love her.

Write a sentence with twenty words about cats:

I have a cat. His name is Mittens. He is black and white.

Write a sentence with twenty words about cats:

Cats are small, furry animals that many people keep as pets.

Write a sentence with twenty words about cats:

I have a cat. His name is Simon and he is very cute.

Write a sentence with twenty words about cats:

I have a cat who likes to sleep on my head at night.

Write a sentence with twenty words about cats:

I have a cat. His name is Mittens. He is fluffy and gray.

Write a sentence with twenty words about cats:

I love cats because they are so cute and cuddly.
